node.text:
Falling in love all over again as we get ready for our special Valentines' sundown date this year ❤️⁣
⁣
We brought our @notyourmothers haircare products to our Island getaway to help us keep our hair healthy and beautiful for our special evening.⁣
⁣
Whatever the occasion may be for you this Valentines, make sure you try and grab their products at your local @walgreens Happy Valentines! #nymIRL
